lead_paragraph: Following is a factbox with reaction to the sacking of England manager Sam Allardyce on Tuesday after he was caught up in a newspaper sting talking about how to get around transfer rules amid a series of injudicious comments.

headline.print_headline: Factbox-Reaction to Sacking of England Manager Allardyce
headline.main: Factbox-Reaction to Sacking of England Manager Allardyce
